## Overview

In this episode of the FluCoMa Podcast, we see part two of my talk with John Bowers. John is an artist-researcher whose work has appeared all over the world. In this second episode, we learn about some of John other projects that notably make use of the FluCoMa tools, and also breach some broader questions around subjects such as HCI, annotation, creating coding environments and performance ecologies.
See part one of this podcast [here](/explore/bowers-1).

